    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>to the pan with your <strong>balsamic sun-dried tomato paste</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 3-4 min or until fragrant</p>",
