    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks (reserve some leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Once the orzo is cooked, add the <strong>chopped spinach </strong>and<strong> chopped basil </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>caponata orzo</strong></p>",
