      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>caponata orzo</strong> with the <strong>roasted aubergine</strong> and <strong>crispy capers</strong> on top</p><p>Garnish with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and the <strong>reserved basil leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
